{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"24795-who-is-our-friend","title":"Who Is Our Friend?","description":"Rhino, Crocodile, Giraffe and Zebra all have an unlikely friend. Can you guess who he is?","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Jade  Mathieson"],"illustrators":["Gerhard Van Wyk"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Book Dash","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/24795-who-is-our-friend"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/706095/size3/61695b92450e5cf6696869c4b800dd6e.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/706095/size6/61695b92450e5cf6696869c4b800dd6e.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86009/size6/8ec96188d9bf93edb201e0146e3aef69.jpg","text":"Can you guess who our best friend is?\nHe’s not like us at all.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86010/size6/a6f477728ce1199724204be6ce4ed7e4.jpg","text":"Our best friend is Bird!","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86011/size6/445042a218d8b4d705b00ea5d6ab235f.jpg","text":"I am Rhino. \nI get covered in fleas.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86012/size6/a3cfaab2aa9bf0e8c2e47b1e229542b4.jpg","text":"Bird eats them all up.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86014/size6/740689ef69454fc5cd8956a7403ce1d2.jpg","text":"I am Crocodile. \nI can’t brush my teeth.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86015/size6/9a5609ed7d4c610369713e5a3b2085f1.jpg","text":"Bird pecks them all clean.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86016/size6/6a146d0286d0afc278c3c86ee1bfdfe4.jpg","text":"I am Giraffe.\nI can’t scratch my head.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86017/size6/2e5d84df70ccb1632c1f82a6727b9e0c.jpg","text":"Bird can reach just the right spot.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86018/size6/1ec43246217c8656e557fa6fad47fb5f.jpg","text":"I am Zebra. \nI can’t see things far away.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86019/size6/f65aa51440c4ab5ea112e8c4826d480f.jpg","text":"Bird has great eyes, \nso when he’s watching I’m safe.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86020/size6/5219910f78bc920973c9c918ba0dd2fd.jpg","text":"Bird might be different, but that’s no problem…","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86021/size6/1bde7620176cdedc3c89618065d717e0.jpg","text":"We don’t even mind when he sings!","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86022/size6/08c3ce24eaa2af91da10c3553964fdb9.jpg","text":"14/15","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86025/size6/e06baf5219eb5399243a8ae62bf34921.jpg","text":"Will you be my friend?","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":14,"words":100}}